<para id="fs-idm156789200">Based on their positions in the periodic table, rank the following atoms in order of increasing first ionization energy: F, Li, N, Rb</para></problem>
<solution id="fs-idm10976144">
<para id="fs-idm151309888">Rb &lt; Li &lt; N &lt; F</para></solution></exercise>
