<para id="fs-idm46185392">Compare both the numbers of protons and electrons present in each to rank the following ions in order of increasing radius: As<sup>3–</sup>, Br<sup>–</sup>, K<sup>+</sup>, Mg<sup>2+</sup>.</para></problem>
